              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "A Primo Geovishap awoken from a centuries-long slumber that can absorb different kinds of elemental power to unleash a Primordial Shower infused with Hydro, Pyro, Cryo, or Electro. If this attack hits a character protected by a <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">shield</span>, the Primo Geovishap will take some DMG in return. If <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">the shield's elemental type is Geo</span> or it <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">matches that of the Primordial Shower</span>, the amount of reflected DMG will be increased..."
